  <priority-name nil="true"></priority-name>
  <original-body>Rails::Generators::Actions#plugin (railties/lib/rails/generators/actions.rb) states that it accepts the :branch option to specify a specific branch from git for a plugin.  This directly conflicts with the accepted options used by the install command of script/rails plugin - see #4117 .  Also, it incorrectly presumes that -b is an accepted command line flag to script/rails plugin install; -r is the correct command line flag.</original-body>
