  <original-body-html>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Rails::Generators::Actions#plugin
(railties/lib/rails/generators/actions.rb) states that it accepts
the :branch option to specify a specific branch from git for a
plugin. This directly conflicts with the accepted options used by
the install command of script/rails plugin - see &lt;a href=
&quot;/projects/8994/tickets/4117&quot; title=&quot;Ticket #4117&quot;&gt;#4117&lt;/a&gt; .
